<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Página No Encontrada | Panadería Artesanal</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/error.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-content">
            <!-- Icon -->
            <div class="error-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                    <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/>
                    <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <!-- Error Code -->
            <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>

            <!-- Error Title -->
            <h2 class="error-title">Página No Encontrada</h2>

            <!-- Error Description -->
            <p class="error-description">
                Lo sentimos, la página que buscas no existe o ha sido movida.
                Puede que el pan se haya horneado en otro horno.
            </p>

            <!-- Actions -->
            <div class="error-actions">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick='location.href="@Url.Action("Index", "PublicMvc")"'>>
                    <svg class="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path d="m3 9 9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
                        <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
                    </svg>
                    Volver al Inicio
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick='location.href="@Url.Action("Index", "PublicMvc")"'>
                    <svg class="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"/>
                        <polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"/>
                    </svg>
                    Página Anterior
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Bread Decoration -->
            <div class="bread-decoration">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 200 100" fill="none">
                    <path d="M20 60 Q50 20, 100 40 T180 60 L180 80 Q100 90, 20 80 Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.1"/>
                    <ellipse cx="50" cy="55" rx="4" ry="3" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.15"/>
                    <ellipse cx="100" cy="50" rx="4" ry="3" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.15"/>
                    <ellipse cx="150" cy="55" rx="4" ry="3" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.15"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
